    <p class="MsoNormal">
      Hi all,<o p="#DEFAULT"></o>
    </p>
    <p class="MsoNormal">
      Thanks for Max Zhuang, ENC/RD Internal Stationery Booking Tool is ready now<o p="#DEFAULT"></o>
    </p>
    <p class="MsoNormal">
      <font color="black"><a href="http://itknj.cn.ao.ericsson.se/max/stationery/productlist.php">http://itknj.cn.ao.ericsson.se/max/stationery/productlist.php</a></font><o p="#DEFAULT"></o>
